snippet.title: Genshin Impact Story Teaser: We Will Be Reunited (Contains spoilers)
snippet.description:
"We will be reunited. But not here, not now."
"We will meet at this journey's end... Once the dust has settled."

Coming Free-to-Play on PlayStation®4 on 9.28.2020
Pre-order the Adventurer's Starter Bundle now on PlayStation™Store

Game pre-registration link: https://genshin.mihoyo.com/pre-register/
